# Note: We want to keep the vault structure but not the obsidian workspace files and logs.
# However, we do want to keep the markdown files in vault. So we ignore specific subdirs.
# Let's be more precise: ignore .obsidian and workspace directories inside vault, but keep .md files.
# We'll ignore the directories themselves.
vault/**/.obsidian/
vault/**/workspace/

